## <a id='deploy-bosh'></a>Step 12: Update Network Availability Zones

Ater BOSH is successfully deployed, update the network you defined above (`NET-MGMT-PKS`) to include each of the COMPUTE AZs that you defined. This ensures that both the Management AZ and the Compute AZs appear in the <%= vars.product_tile %> tile for the Plans.

1. Return to the BOSH tile and click **Create Networks**.

    <%= image_tag("images/nsxt/bosh/config-bosh-26.png") %>

1. Edit the network (`NET-MGMT-PKS`) and each COMPUTE AZ.

    <%= image_tag("images/nsxt/bosh/config-bosh-27.png") %>

1. Click Save.

    <%= image_tag("images/nsxt/bosh/config-bosh-28.png") %>

1. Review pending changes, and click **Apply Changes** to redeploy BOSH.

